{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/testOptionIsolateDirs","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"testOptionIsolateDirs","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String"}],"symbolKind":"var","role":"symbol","title":"testOptionIsolateDirs","roleHeading":"Global Variable","externalID":"s:4GLib21testOptionIsolateDirsSSvp"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/testoptionisolatedirs"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A value that can be passed as an option to [func"},{"code":"GLib.test_init","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"testOptionIsolateDirs","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates a unique temporary directory for each unit test and uses sets"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"XDG directories to point into subdirectories of it for the duration of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the unit test. The directory tree is cleaned up after the test finishes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"successfully."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that this doesn’t take effect until [func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.test_run"},{"type":"text","text":"] is called,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"so calls to (for example) [func","type":"text"},{"code":"GLib.get_home_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] will return the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"system-wide value when made in a test program’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"main()"},{"type":"text","text":" function."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The following functions will return subdirectories of the temporary directory","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when this option is used. The specific subdirectory paths in use are not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"guaranteed to be stable API — always use a getter function to retrieve them."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"code":"GLib.get_home_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.get_user_cache_dir"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.get_system_config_dirs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.get_user_config_dir"},{"text":"]","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.get_system_data_dirs","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"]","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.get_user_data_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"]","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"GLib.get_user_state_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"]","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.get_user_runtime_dir"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The subdirectories may not be created by the test harness; as with normal","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calls to functions like [func"},{"code":"GLib.get_user_cache_dir","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"], the caller must"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be prepared to create the directory if it doesn’t exist."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/testOptionIsolateDirs":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A value that can be passed as an option to [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.test_init"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"testOptionIsolateDirs","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"}],"role":"symbol","title":"testOptionIsolateDirs","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/testoptionisolatedirs","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/testOptionIsolateDirs"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/glib","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","type":"topic"}}}